body.p:
The following actions are available when you hover the edits in the Review view, using the cursor:
Remove Action available for highlights and comments presented in the Review view. Use this action to remove these highlights or comments from your document;
Accept Action available for inserted and deleted content presented in the Review view. Use this action to accept the changes in your document;
Reject Action available for inserted and deleted content presented in the Review view. Use this action to reject the changes in your document.
